text: Taeniurops is a genus of stingrays in the family Dasyatidae. Its two species were formerly contained within the genus Taeniura. ==Species== * Taeniurops grabata (Geoffroy Saint-Hilaire, 1817) (Round fantail stingray) * Taeniurops meyeni (Müller & Henle, 1841) (Round ribbontail ray) ==References== Category:Dasyatidae
title: Taeniurops
